  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is all inclusive with breakfast, lunch, dinner and drinks included. Meals start with dinner on the first evening and end with breakfast on the last morning.</p>
<p>Each morning you can enjoy an extensive breakfast buffet with a range of sweet and savoury items including additional hot options, served between <span>7:30-9:30pm.</span></p>
<p>Lunch is served buffet style in the main restaurant and includes a variety of salads, hot dishes, cheese and desserts.  A picnic option can be requested at an additional supplement. Lunch is served between <span>12:30-13:30pm. </span></p>
<p><span>Evening meals are served buffet style in the main restaurant and includes a range of salads, hot dishes, cheese and desserts. If you fancy mixing it up a bit, you can enjoy one meal at the </span><span>'Le Mont Blanc' restaurant serving Savoyard specialities and one meal at the Italian style Petit Zinc. R</span>eserve your table upon arrival at the club, please note that meals at Le Mont Blanc and Petit Zinc are limited to one time during your stay.<span> Dinner is served between 19:00-21:00pm.</span></p>
<p>Light snacks are available from the bar, and typically includes <span>cheese/charcuterie, chips and sweets.</span></p>
<p><span>Christmas eve and New Years eve gala dinners are included. </span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Drinks</strong></p>
<p>The bar is open 7 days a week and provisional opening times are 10am to midnight. After the bar closes there's a coffee/tea/water self service station available until the breakfast buffet service starts at 7am.</p>
<p>Drinks at the bar include beers, cocktails, soft drinks, wine by the glass and hot drinks. Premium bottled beer, premium spirits/cocktails and bottles of wine are not included but can be purchased if required.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
